
0.2.4

  - more efficient git support for versioning markup codes
  - more detailed documentation of record and units types
  - links to type definitions from occurrences of those types
  - new options to include HTML in title page and disable links to source files

0.2.3

 - file names in config files can now be quoted
 - new option to display designated top modules separately in hierarchy view
 - backlinks from design units to units that instantiate them
 - experimental git support for @version, @date, @author and @id markups
 - fixes for Windows: quoting of path separators, install as .pl, environment variable instructions

0.2.2

 - limited support for PSL (Accelera Property Specification Language)
 - optional recursive source file search in directories
 - table indentation and cell padding now adjustable by CSS instead of command-line options

0.2.1
 - syntax markup with CSS classes which can be overridden by user style file
 - source markup pages generated by VHDocL, or by JS generated by it
 - markup in documentation page code quotes consistent with source page markup
 - HTML footer option for copyright notices or similar
 - function and procedure documentation sections merged
 - deduplication of declarations in package and package body; omitting of empty package bodies
 - recursive open/close added to instantiation hierarchy view

0.2.0
 - parser rewrite for more efficiency
 - source pages with syntax highlighting and source list
 - hierarchical list for instantiation overview / hierarchy

0.1beta5
 - fixed wrong source file links

0.1beta4
 - worked around abs2rel() bug in fixpath()
 - fixed typos in documentation

0.1beta3
 - allow "=" between option and argument but disallowed directly following
   arguments which might be confused with bundled options
 - use File::Path::mkpath() for creating output directory

0.1beta2
 - regexes parsing for..use statements and generic/port maps corrected
 - bugs in parsing argument and sensitivity lists fixed
 - fixed erroneous duplicates in instantiation hierarchy
 - added search for binding in the absence of component declarations
 - minor fixes and improvements of HTML output
 - subversion keywords removed from substitutions
 - replaced die statements by function which does not print source line numbers

0.1beta1
 - first revision as VHDocL

0.1alpha
 - initial revision under the name VNV


